%Section: Education
\vspace{5 pt}\section{Research Interests}
\justify{My research interests lie in \textsc{robust} and \textsc{formally verifiable} machine learning. I study the landscape adversarial examples, towards verifiable robustness while maintaining high accuracy. I am also interested in the generation of practical adversarial examples, neural network verification, and the intersection of explainable/interpretable with robust ML.}

